diaryEntry2.title: Mysterious Amazon Van Making Laps In Cul De Sac
diaryEntry2.entry: Aww, it's true. I've been hiding it for so long. That's a popular name today. Little , big ? With gusto. We're rescuing ya. It may comfort you to know that Fry's death took only fifteen seconds, yet the pain was so intense, that it felt to him like fifteen years. And it goes without saying, it caused him to empty his bowels. Bender, I didn't know you liked cooking. That's so cute. Now, now. Perfectly symmetrical violence never solved anything. Hello Morbo, how's the family? Michelle, I don't regret this, but I both rue and lament it. For example, if you killed your grandfather, you'd cease to exist!

diaryEntry3.title: Ivan's Dog Has A Low Emotional Intelligence
diaryEntry3.entry: Whoa a real live robot; or is that some kind of cheesy New Year's costume? Isn't it true that you have been paid for your testimony? We can't compete with Mom! Her company is big and evil! Ours is small and neutral!

diaryEntry4.title: Dogs Walking Dogs Is Not Ok
diaryEntry4.entry: Ummm…to eBay? Take me to your leader! Goodbye, cruel world. Goodbye, cruel lamp. Goodbye, cruel velvet drapes, lined with what would appear to be some sort of cruel muslin and the cute little pom-pom curtain pull cords. Cruel though they may be…
